The graph in \fullref{fig:planarcycleofcuts} is planar, so the fact
that it is not RAAGedy could have also been deduced 
by applying a theorem of Nguyen and Tran \cite{NguTra19}.
The graph in \fullref{fig:nonplanarcycleofcuts} is nonplanar, so
